# Web3Forms access key — required for the quote-request form.
#
# To obtain one:
#   1. Go to https://web3forms.com
#   2. Enter sales@evolve-sensing.com as the destination email
#   3. Web3Forms emails you a UUID access key
#   4. Copy this file to .env (it's gitignored) and paste the key below
#
# The key is public-safe: it only authorises delivery to the pre-configured
# destination and cannot be used to redirect leads elsewhere. See
# src/lib/web3forms.ts for full security rationale.
#
# For GitHub Pages deployment, set this as a repository secret named
# VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY and reference it in .github/workflows/deploy.yml.
VITE_WEB3FORMS_KEY=your-web3forms-access-key-here
